messages.message:
Hello! Who is the best person to ask for help setting up a subdomain that I can use for a landing page?

Context: My latest engineering project is learning how to use Mailchimp :smile: I'm trying to set up a landing page for our Series B announcement. The easiest way to do everything we want to will be though Mailchimp. Here are the instructions for using a custom domain with Mailchimp: https://mailchimp.com/help/landing-page-domains/
